{"tid":1635679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足裝修對大集團影響甚微 (Forward TG保險界小薯)","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:02:23.000Z","uid":222569,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d47ba299468dd138aee796cf89745bedb3e9485","tid":1635679,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"轉<br />\n<br />\n我係一名保險界小薯。近日見到有好多有關緊急法令保險失效嘅消息，想澄清一下：<br />\n<br />\n手足裝修對大集團影響甚微<br />\n<br />\n手足徹底裝修完一間舖，大集團損失嘅只係一個比例極細嘅墊底費（幾皮野咁上下囉），但係換來係全新嘅裝修（保單保障為回復全新狀 new for old ）。<br />\n<br />\n停業零損失<br />\n<br />\n你以為可以令間舖停業，集團會損失舖租同營業額？少年，你太年輕了！大集團全險一般有加購「營業中斷保險 Business interruption」。換言之，停業損失嘅營業額係有得賠嘅！仲要係同上年同期一樣！簡單啲講，係零成本坐响度收錢！甚至對沖咗手足努力罷食罷買嘅成果！<br />\n<br />\n但係手足付出嘅，係巨大嘅受傷同被捕嘅風險！我地見到你地咁努力但係損失嘅唔係嗰啲黑集團，我地好心痛，好唔抵呀！<br />\n<br />\n緊急法下保險失效<br />\n<br />\n呢個說法源於一般財產全險（Property All Risk PAR)下，一個基本會有嘅不保事項（General Exclusions）：「Riots and civil commotion (RCC)」。即係如果損失源自(cause)係同RCC有關的話，保單就唔會賠償損失。<br />\n<br />\n呢個係一般商戶/住家居買保險幾乎必定有嘅。<br />\n<br />\n但係大集團黎講，佢地份保險單係度身訂造嘅。有好多大集團都會加購一啲附加條款。<br />\n<br />\n各大集團（例如：銀行、牛奶公司、富臨、優品360、黨鐵同近期裝修大戶美心集團）嘅保單，其實都有加購對RCC嘅保障。<br />\n<br />\n重點要來了：<br />\n<br />\n總結而言：黑裝修對大集團商舖嘅損失幾乎微乎其微，甚至乎益左佢！<br />\n<br />\n推介：「罷食罷買」方為上策！<br />\n<br />\n香港做生意最大成本係咩？係舖租同人工。有咩慘得過白俾燈油火蠟舖租人工，但係拍烏蠅呢？仲要我地係零成本啊！留返啲氣力去對付班動物啦！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"6c3895c8ade916b892244d7dcdec8af2b86a76fb","tid":1635679,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"4a96007125d218428fcffb3e4c20b434208d5fd5","tid":1635679,"uid":38109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n下年保費實加啦<br />\n<br />\n死5毛"},{"pid":"2318ce4ac0f45fd85edf6b5700ad3f79214f5337","tid":1635679,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"起下底就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31674005b2b4e3b8fd94346dacecc9ff4b50a73","tid":1635679,"uid":29599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"又開多個一樣既post <br />\n沉底啦仆街"},{"pid":"4d01061f58afca9d4cd29e2382852eb97cac7868","tid":1635679,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d8dc10918abe717d62602fc4d620541fd6f4c1","tid":1635679,"uid":269918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638361b53512443e550ed955704640a66e101c67","tid":1635679,"uid":269918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb32e064e2dba43e99aa8cbef115dcc3cbfe22a","tid":1635679,"uid":269918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}